$$= P\left(Z \geq \frac{65}{130}\right) = P(Z \geq 0.5)$$

Using the standard normal table:
- P(Z ≤ 0.5) = 0.6915
- P(Z ≥ 0.5) = 1 - 0.6915 = 0.3085

