Solution: I need to find P(A₁ ∪ A₂ ∪ A₃) using Theorem 1.1-6, which is the inclusion-exclusion principle.

**Theorem 1.1-6 (Inclusion-Exclusion Principle):**
For three events:
P(A₁ ∪ A₂ ∪ A₃) = P(A₁) + P(A₂) + P(A₃) - P(A₁ ∩ A₂) - P(A₁ ∩ A₃) - P(A₂ ∩ A₃) + P(A₁ ∩ A₂ ∩ A₃)

