- P(A₂) = 1/3
- P(A₃) = 1/3
- P(A₁ ∩ A₂) = (1/3)² = 1/9
- P(A₁ ∩ A₃) = (1/3)² = 1/9
- P(A₂ ∩ A₃) = (1/3)² = 1/9
- P(A₁ ∩ A₂ ∩ A₃) = (1/3)³ = 1/27

**Calculation:**
P(A₁ ∪ A₂ ∪ A₃) = 1/3 + 1/3 + 1/3 - 1/9 - 1/9 - 1/9 + 1/27

Converting to a common denominator (27):
