P(A₁ ∪ A₂ ∪ A₃) = (9 + 9 + 9 - 3 - 3 - 3 + 1)/27

P(A₁ ∪ A₂ ∪ A₃) = (27 - 9 + 1)/27 = 19/27

Converting to decimal: 19/27 ≈ 0.7037

